Sentencas: We propose a system that combines a seal-less planar solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) stack and polymer electrolyte fuel cell (PEFC) stack.
Titulo: Numerical evaluation of a parallel fuel feeding SOFC-PEFC system using seal-less planar SOFC stack

Sentencas: In the proposed system, fuel for the SOFC (SOFC fuel) and fuel for the PEFC (PEFC fuel) are fed to each stack in parallel.
Titulo: Numerical evaluation of a parallel fuel feeding SOFC-PEFC system using seal-less planar SOFC stack

Sentencas: The steam reformer for the PEFC fuel surrounds the scal-less planar SOFC stack.
Titulo: Numerical evaluation of a parallel fuel feeding SOFC-PEFC system using seal-less planar SOFC stack

Sentencas: Combustion exhaust heat from the SOFC stack is used for reforming the PEFC fuel.
Titulo: Numerical evaluation of a parallel fuel feeding SOFC-PEFC system using seal-less planar SOFC stack

Sentencas: We show that the electrical efficiency in the SOFC-PEFC system is 5% higher than that in a simple SOFC system using only a seal-less planar SOFC stack when the SOFC operation temperature is higher than 973 K. (c) 2005
Titulo: Numerical evaluation of a parallel fuel feeding SOFC-PEFC system using seal-less planar SOFC stack
